title.narrative: Meatco Foundation- GRANT-Rangeland and Marketing Development Support Project (RMDSP-NCA)

description.narrative: -To improve the awareness and active involvement of key stakeholders at the local, regional and national levels in climate change adaptation strategies related to rangeland, livestock, marketing and cropping. To support locally established organisations to develop regionally appropriate responses to improve uptake of increased production of fodder, improved herd productivity as well as increased sales of livestock.-To improve the whole chain of production of livestock farmers in selected sites
